title: How to use GPT-3 to parse free-text documents
Revealer for Twitter
text: If you're a Twitter user who loves sharing images, you'll love this new product! With Many users on Twitter share images like analytics, stats, and reading material, you can set goals like the number of likes and replies. After breaking those targets into small targets, each time the small target is achieved, this revealer_bot will tweet with the given image with blur opacity set according to the progress.
